{"tid":1532969,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聽］保護學生 學生自保","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:35:56.000Z","uid":73959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6337d0448995c3b426113a43937ac17ecf25ab6a","tid":1532969,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"首先要向所有今日有罷課或者表態嘅中學生致敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知新一代嘅你哋好堅 係戰鬥民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係今時唔同往日<br />\n學校係<span style=\"color: red;\">好撚好撚黑暗</span><br />\n記住呢句：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">冇任何人信得過，除咗你自己。</span></strong><br />\n校長可以報警去圍返自己學生<br />\n證明咗一樣嘢：<br />\n閂埋校門 你點呼天叫地都冇人知<br />\n唔係要自我審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢個時候要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">智取</span>！<br />\n要革命成功 必定要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鬥長命</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">革命係可以用其他方法無聲無息地喺校園輸出</span></span></strong><br />\n唔一定要咁張揚俾所有人知道你嘅底牌係咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除非</span>你認為自己內心非常強大<br />\n唔怕被退學、反欺凌、被刻意留難<br />\n甚至敢屌返班藍絲老師<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">否則</span>請學生們平日好好保護自己<br />\n唔好向老師/社工直接表達你係咩立場<br />\n因為你哋仲有更多嘅機會發揮<br />\n最後，<ins>保重身體</ins>，共勉之。"},{"pid":"4b31583c5880ef2ca289916f0f18a84b8aacdc6e","tid":1532969,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"Btw<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵職員<br />\n今日你包庇唔交CCTV<br />\n他日你自己必定遭殃</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">譴責黨鐵 黑箱作業<br />\n放警入閘 狂毆乘客</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1f2455dbc73caf35c1bc98e5a47767746f8f62bd","tid":1532969,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ec9de4f2a05938e267ba90c0b159cb3cadddc8c7","tid":1532969,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:56:37.000Z","msg":"學生無罪"},{"pid":"edfe2d29c5f7f76bc307bde365f02d96e487df48","tid":1532969,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"反對校園白色恐怖"},{"pid":"cd7c64e2cccc00d61512fe15e6dd8fb7d2ba4d74","tid":1532969,"uid":21761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:58:31.000Z","msg":"四圍寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd90b6ae64c2ede6807a6d68cc16f9a72d96e2a","tid":1532969,"uid":133207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b31583c5880ef2ca289916f0f18a84b8aacdc6e","tid":1532969,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"Btw<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵職員<br />\n今日你包庇唔交CCTV<br />\n他日你自己必定遭殃</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">譴責黨鐵 黑箱作業<br />\n放警入閘 狂毆乘客</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:34:54.000Z","msg":"全民跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185d42c81c09273f26ede213b8e78584039c247b","tid":1532969,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:35:56.000Z","msg":"9月3添馬三罷"}]}